<br>
&quot;Ares, you are VERY misinformed about my involvement in this petty little war.  I NEVER told Hypnos that I would intercede on his side.  I only get involved in wars on two conditions.  One it is an outward threat to Olympus.  Second if it is an internal threat it will completely change and unbalance the power structure.  This conflict does not qualify as either situation.  I told him the same thing.  So whoever you got your information from is wrong.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He then folds his arms:: &quot;If I were to bring my Army of Dead or Undead.  You would NOT have any power over them, even in this plane.  They would claim Alliegance to whomever I did.  Just the fact that you would have the audacity to make such a proclomation I should bring them up here and crush you!  But...I will not.  Not this day anyway.  Perhaps another.&quot;<br>
